&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Participate in or lead key meetings with internal and external stakeholders with or on behalf of the CEO, shaping program design and execution and ensuring that initiatives are executed to the highest standard.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
